snippet.textDisplay: 'Obak Bhalobasha' Warfaze's album from 1992, which was released 8 years before I was born. I have been listening to Warfaze since I was 10 years old. The first time I went to Cox's Bazar was in 2016. It was a moonlit night. We were 5 friends together, singing this song by the sea around 1:00 AM. Ah, what a feeling it was. I can't describe it. I miss those days. Today, I saw Babna Korim for the first time. Salute to Babna Sir and Warfaze for making our adolescence beautiful. Thanks a lot to Coke Studio Bangla for presenting us with such a wonderful performance. Especially for bringing Babna Sir. Hats off!!
snippet.textOriginal: 'Obak Bhalobasha' Warfaze's album from 1992, which was released 8 years before I was born. I have been listening to Warfaze since I was 10 years old.
